title: The Capitol Classic - A Bicycle Ride & Race for Au
GrandStay Criterium
description: Criterium in downtown St Cloud, MN
registration: Registration starts at 8AM and closes 15 minutes before each race.
notes: Entry fee is $20 and $8 for a second race.
directions: Only an hour from the Twin Cities. From I94 take Hwy 15 N exit;follow Hwy 15 to Division St/Hwy 23 and take a right. Continue on Division to 4th Avenue and take a left;follow 4th three blocks to 1st St N, go two blocks to 7th St-you will see registration in Court House Square to your left.
